item.title: Prayer bpn12472 in Namibia
item.description: Nye ava ta Mutalelifa oipala yeni ku Kalunga! Keleleni omesho eni ahatale oinima ili li, nye mwa talelife kouhamba wefimano lo mafimano aeshe. Oye aeke mupula aishe ei mwa hala; oYe aeke mukonga emupe aishe tamukongo. Lumwe aluke oha yandye elinekelo li fike pefele lwe yovi, lumwe aluke ohavelula omikifi ihadi veluka lwefe lweyovi, lumwe oha talaleke oiveta, nekomono lokomutwe ohamangulula omutima komapando owi. Ohaningi eshi ta ningi, fye oshike hatuningi?
